0. Ensure that you have already setup user authentication using make:auth

1. Go into .env to setup the email setting.

MAIL_DRIVER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=smtp.mailchimp
MAIL_PORT=2525
MAIL_USERNAME=fcf8b7f60b0ca0
MAIL_PASSWORD=53f05ecccfa9e2
MAIL_ENCRYPTION=null

2. restart server

3. During testing using your local server, when you hit the reset password button in your email, you may recieve an error, if this
happens go into the browser and append "8000" to http://localhost/password/reset/
